stats

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • stats.Profile

  • public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a user's profile. Its fields are normal arrays of stats and an HttpRequest object corresponding to his or her profile.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Profile(HttpRequest myUserHttp)
      Constructs a profile object and initializes all the stats to new arrays.
